*libwacom-0.7 (28 Mar 2013)

  28 Mar 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +libwacom-0.7.ebuild:
  Version bump for Gnome 3.8

  06 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc, wrt bug #449220

  01 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  Add ~alpha, wrt bug #449220

  01 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  Add ~ia64, wrt bug #449220

  28 Nov 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.5.ebuild,
  libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  Use udev.eclass and virtual/udev.

  23 Sep 2012; Anthony G. Basile <blueness@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  Keyword ~arm for gnome-settings-daemon

  23 Sep 2012; Anthony G. Basile <blueness@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  keyword ~ppc, bug #379651

  23 Sep 2012; Anthony G. Basile <blueness@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  keyword ~ppc64, bug #379651

*libwacom-0.6 (15 Sep 2012)

  15 Sep 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -libwacom-0.4.ebuild, +libwacom-0.6.ebuild:
  Version bump with better Bamboo series support; use pkgconfig to read udevdir
  from udev.pc. Drop old.

*libwacom-0.5 (19 May 2012)

  19 May 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  +libwacom-0.5.ebuild, +files/libwacom-0.5-eraser.patch,
  +files/libwacom-0.5-eraser-bamboo.patch:
  Version bump for bug #416363, thanks to Christoph Brill (egore). Now properly
  installs udev rules.

  04 May 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> libwacom-0.4.ebuild:
  dev-util/pkgconfig -> virtual/pkgconfig

*libwacom-0.4 (06 Apr 2012)

  06 Apr 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  +libwacom-0.4.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
  New ebuild for a library to identify Wacom tablet features; used by
  gnome-3.4.
